Sup fam, im back on track just like few months ago and here i am still, piled with bunch of works to do over 50+ish designs that i have to do (dont ask me why okay, i keep on taking requests again god i need to stop). So here's a design that i made quite a long ago, its a remake from the design that i made before and i have to say it really is fun to design this one, well every photography in general cause i dont know, it feels far different than just making a new logo like what i've been doing all this time for 3-4 years straight. Expect some more of designs like this soon cause i've been interested in fashion design too lately, tried some street wear layering and lookin really nice on me and i can't wait to take another self portrait design with it, super excited. I also wanna ask about me making a personal account? Cause i dont know if any of you guys are here to see all of my designs and just wanna follow me for my personal things, its also so that i can know how popular i am and my follower progress, Cause designers need popularity to gain more customers so, yea.
